{"hd1a6f5f5g8894g49d4g83f9g7433c7561541": ["You think you saved us? You just prolonged the inevitable.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "9f869784-6ddc-b41b-c884-08be8ecfdb98"], "hc11be85cgaf7cg4264g9839g66df774bd08f": ["Sooner or later, other outsiders will bring trouble to the grove.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "720db670-a14e-256a-8517-dac8dc7a82d0"], "hc756c7b9g7b92g418agad38g072d7017b1d9": ["This will happen again. We won't have you to rescue us when it does.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "f7579297-145e-e39a-9497-a6ab149a3cd3"], "h363f5051g5f6bg48cag85a0ga99831033f00": ["Kagha was right. We must put ourselves first.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "bfb2bf2e-1d2b-5d23-4bdf-f641778f5551"], "h69f3abe6gf817g4108g8905g55677a4f38c4": ["She's dead because of your meddling.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "1f5e515a-3d2d-6cbc-76c0-da69673af7e4"], "h98c6a1ccgac1bg4864gaca3g28eb9c49215e": ["You had no right to intervene. You're not one of us.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "a6f6e4fa-55e0-899a-bae4-811fd8b0c593"], "he289e910g278bg4d70g843ag4f9be91e6eb9": ["I've got nothing to say to you, outsider.", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "bcc54734-dc49-9ae6-978f-e533d6806416"], "h5533b7acg134fg4243gb55fgd41ff215a7a2": ["<i>In umbram cretus, sanguine iuratus.</i>", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "563079cc-a5f3-f1ad-9898-ba8a4c0b1d67"], "he4ba6335g9d6cg4e24gb9b4g6b808eb21c76": ["<i>Ab spiritu humoque, aculeus vitisque.</i>", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "d01f855b-0256-145a-a6ac-17c70c36b3b5"], "h8512f896gfd07g4df7ga43cgf38c8848224f": ["<i>Complexum tuum, ab terra ortum, ad nos defer.</i>", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "ccf6b04e-d964-1a6c-e208-6aed5cad9466"], "h0996958cgd33fg41d5gad02gf16968877bb2": ["<i>Defende nos ab imminentibus aequilibrio tuo.</i>", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "f849d133-52fb-0a71-4af3-ab573f0143ee"], "he905be13g4ef6g4b3fgadabg4b1f56ff9db7": ["<i>Hostes subeunt. Protege nos. Muni nos.</i>", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "70f0e717-9ed2-23ba-2cbd-8c6dc90fb262"], "hc5f433b3g6562g4e30gb10ag261cae5395f6": ["<i>Aggeniculamur in umbra tua, Pater Arborum.</i>", "641fc4b5-3c42-4c4d-a759-541ad437f9df", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid5.html", "36b95f31-eccd-f56c-97d6-c4b12468f48f"]}